{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_014VHLf1dcNqeta7DsXeizPT","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01YVv4WW4rqbN6yedZU9H4xe","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","old_string":"- **CRITICAL: Dev agent corrupted sprint-state.json** — tests or writeStateAtomic() calls during dev overwrote the real sprint-state.json with a 2-story test fixture. Had to restore from ralph/.state-snapshot.json. The YAML auto-generation side effect in writeStateAtomic() is dangerous when called during tests.","new_string":"- **CRITICAL: Dev agent corrupted sprint-state.json** — tests or writeStateAtomic() calls during dev overwrote the real sprint-state.json with a 2-story test fixture. Had to restore from ralph/.state-snapshot.json. The YAML auto-generation side effect in writeStateAtomic() is dangerous when called during tests.\n\n### 11-2-sprint-status-yaml-derived-view — code-review (2026-03-24T11:18Z)\n\n- HIGH (fixed): Test filesystem corruption — sprint-yaml.test.ts, state.test.ts, index.test.ts all wrote to real project dir. Converted to tmpdir isolation.\n- MEDIUM (fixed): Platform-incompatible path handling — used string slicing instead of dirname().\n- MEDIUM (fixed): Missing edge case tests — added 4 new tests for non-standard keys, empty dir, YAML write failures.\n- LOW (not fixed): run.ts still constructs sprintStatusPath for YAML in Ralph prompt.\n- LOW (not fixed): parseStoryKey not exported, yamlStatus has no exhaustiveness check.\n- **CRITICAL (PERSISTS): sprint-state.json and sprint-status.yaml corrupted AGAIN during code review despite tmpdir isolation fix.** Tests are still somehow writing to the real project directory. The test isolation is incomplete or some test path bypasses the tmpdir chdir."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":235,"cache_read_input_tokens":64762,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":235},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"bd5543f6-f408-4218-88bd-6e3bcdc37563","uuid":"5d382af5-b205-42b9-8757-99d6c7b63aad"}
